org.apache.hadoop.net

类 InnerNodeImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.net.NodeBase
      • org.apache.hadoop.net.InnerNodeImpl
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    org.apache.hadoop.net.InnerNode, org.apache.hadoop.net.Node

    public class InnerNodeImpl
extends org.apache.hadoop.net.NodeBase
implements org.apache.hadoop.net.InnerNode
    InnerNode represents a switch/router of a data center or rack. Different from a leaf node, it has non-null children.
